{"tid":1510302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位一定要忍","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:59:40.000Z","uid":84275,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05b9027fcf125f9b1b06eb95f8d6dd2d450b8448","tid":1510302,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:37:26.000Z","msg":"請各位忍讓，時間係我地呢邊，等唔到既係七十大壽既老人家<br />\n由而家起停止一切勇武行動，直到十月一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再送頭，唔好再比人拉<br />\n<br />\n一黎比時間林鄭以為局勢開始平靜而鬆懈<br />\n<br />\n二黎政府豬隊友每日都會出錯出醜，每一次出錯出醜都係為我地提供子彈<br />\n<br />\n三黎都睇到開始每個星期少人，就算捱到去十一，義士們都五癆七傷，拉既拉傷既傷，不如休息儲氣，如果你話我都預左比人拉要坐監，咁就學曾蔭權話齋玩舖勁，好過每星期無意義地化成一堆被捕者數字，無意思嫁，而玩舖勁係需要時間去醞釀同預備...<br />\n<br />\n四黎身邊黃屍又好藍屍又好已經開始攰，開始有逃避呢個話題既跡象，係時候比佢地透一啖氣再一次過draw返佢地attention <br />\n<br />\n各位，來日方長，留有用之身抗爭，好過今日就比人拉左，我知大家當中大部分都好醒識得走位，亦有自信自己唔會比人拉，但有時都要為身邊同路人著想<br />\n有用既，玩一次好過浪費精力玩十次"},{"pid":"3e5f22f38179ca5bfbc11481791a8bca937e80cb","tid":1510302,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=66b2f1e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=0fb2a44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=f8b2498b\" data-auto-link